{"id":8724,"date":"2026-02-03T10:31:13","date_gmt":"2026-02-03T03:31:13","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=8724"},"modified":"2026-02-03T10:35:00","modified_gmt":"2026-02-03T03:35:00","slug":"chiet-xuat-re-cam-thao-lam-diu-sang-da-va-giam-viem-tu-nhien","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/su-kien\/chiet-xuat-re-cam-thao-lam-diu-sang-da-va-giam-viem-tu-nhien\/","title":{"rendered":"Chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t r\u1ec5 cam th\u1ea3o &#8211; l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu, s\u00e1ng da v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u1eeb h\u01a1n 2000 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, cam th\u1ea3o (Glycyrrhiza glabra) \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng trong y h\u1ecdc c\u1ed5 truy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu v\u00e0 kh\u00e1ng vi\u00eam. Trong m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t r\u1ec5 cam th\u1ea3o tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u201cng\u00f4i sao t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean\u201d gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m k\u00edch \u1ee9ng, l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y bong tr\u00f3c nh\u01b0 acid t\u1ea9y da.<\/span><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tong-quan-ve-chiet-xuat-re-cam-thao\"><\/span><b>T\u1ed5ng quan v\u1ec1 Chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t r\u1ec5 cam th\u1ea3o<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u00ean khoa h\u1ecdc: Glycyrrhiza glabra (Licorice Root Extract)<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c: L\u00e0 chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t t\u1eeb r\u1ec5 c\u00e2y cam th\u1ea3o, h\u1ecd Fabaceae, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thu h\u00e1i, s\u1ea5y kh\u00f4 v\u00e0 tinh chi\u1ebft ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t tan trong n\u01b0\u1edbc ho\u1eb7c c\u1ed3n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t ch\u00ednh:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Glabridin \u2013 polyphenol c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1ee9c ch\u1ebf enzyme tyrosinase (li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh melanin).<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Licochalcone A \u2013 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb7c t\u00ednh ch\u1ed1ng vi\u00eam, ch\u1ed1ng oxy h\u00f3a m\u1ea1nh, gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ecf v\u00e0 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng da.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Glycyrrhizic acid (Glycyrrhizin) \u2013 c\u00f3 t\u00ednh l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu, gi\u1ea3m ng\u1ee9a, gi\u1ea3m s\u01b0ng vi\u00eam.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u00ean th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn: Licorice Root Extract, Glabridin, Licochalcone A.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-8726 size-full\" style=\"font-size: 16px\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Chiet-xuat-cam-thao-2.webp\" alt=\"R\u1ec5 cam th\u1ea3o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng l\u00e2u \u0111\u1eddi trong y h\u1ecdc c\u1ed5 truy\u1ec1n\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Chiet-xuat-cam-thao-2.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Chiet-xuat-cam-thao-2-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Chiet-xuat-cam-thao-2-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Chiet-xuat-cam-thao-2-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><\/h2>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dac-diem-chiet-xuat-re-cam-thao\"><\/span><b>\u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m Chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t r\u1ec5 cam th\u1ea3o<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cong-dung-noi-bat\"><\/span><b>C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t r\u1ec5 cam th\u1ea3o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n \u0111a n\u0103ng nh\u1edd v\u1eeba l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu, v\u1eeba l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng, v\u1eeba ch\u1ed1ng oxy ho\u00e1:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e0m s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u da: nh\u1edd \u1ee9c ch\u1ebf enzyme tyrosinase, glabridin gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh melanin, c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n th\u00e2m n\u00e1m v\u00e0 s\u1ea1m da.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecf: licochalcone A \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00f2a ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng vi\u00eam, th\u00edch h\u1ee3p cho da \u0111ang k\u00edch \u1ee9ng, m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam ho\u1eb7c sau treatment.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ed1ng oxy ho\u00e1: trung h\u00f2a g\u1ed1c t\u1ef1 do, b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 t\u1ebf b\u00e0o kh\u1ecfi stress oxy ho\u00e1 do tia UV v\u00e0 \u00f4 nhi\u1ec5m.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da: glycyrrhizic acid gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c ch\u00e2m ch\u00edch, b\u1ecfng r\u00e1t.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m: l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, \u00edt g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng, th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng trong m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i ho\u1eb7c sau peel.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-8727 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Chiet-xuat-cam-thao-3.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Chiet-xuat-cam-thao-3.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Chiet-xuat-cam-thao-3-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Chiet-xuat-cam-thao-3-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Chiet-xuat-cam-thao-3-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"co-che-hoat-dong\"><\/span><b>C\u01a1 ch\u1ebf ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e1c flavonoid v\u00e0 saponin trong cam th\u1ea3o ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng theo nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 ch\u1ebf:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Glabridin \u1ee9c ch\u1ebf enzyme tyrosinase v\u00e0 c\u00e1c t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u1ebf b\u00e0o li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p melanin, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 gi\u1ea3m s\u1ea1m da m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y bong tr\u00f3c.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Licochalcone A \u1ee9c ch\u1ebf c\u00e1c cytokine g\u00e2y vi\u00eam (nh\u01b0 IL-6, TNF-\u03b1) v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a g\u1ed1c t\u1ef1 do.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Glycyrrhizic acid \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00e0ng t\u1ebf b\u00e0o, gi\u1ea3m ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 l\u00e0nh th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1ecf.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p l\u1ea1i, chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t cam th\u1ea3o gi\u00fap da \u00eam, s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u h\u01a1n m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dang-bao-che-thuong-gap\"><\/span><b>D\u1ea1ng b\u00e0o ch\u1ebf th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Serum, essence, toner s\u00e1ng da: th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ee9a 0,5\u20132% chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t cam th\u1ea3o ho\u1eb7c 0,1\u20130,5% glabridin tinh khi\u1ebft.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kem ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i\/gi\u1ea3m k\u00edch \u1ee9ng: ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng panthenol, allantoin, madecassoside.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ho\u1eb7c d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ban ng\u00e0y: k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p licochalcone A \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m stress UV.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu: c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m k\u00e8m HA, niacinamide.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"luu-y-su-dung-san-pham-chua-chiet-xuat-re-cam-thao\"><\/span><b>L\u01b0u \u00fd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ee9a Chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t r\u1ec5 cam th\u1ea3o<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"doi-tuong-su-dung\"><\/span><b>\u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da th\u00e2m s\u1ea1m, kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u, n\u00e1m nh\u1eb9 ho\u1eb7c PIH (th\u00e2m sau vi\u00eam).<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ecf r\u00e1t, k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da d\u1ea7u m\u1ee5n c\u00f3 vi\u00eam, c\u1ea7n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t vi\u00eam nh\u1eb9 m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f4 r\u00e1t.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da sau peel, laser, retinoid \u2013 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i v\u00e0 l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8728\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8728\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8728 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Chiet-xuat-cam-thao-4.webp\" alt=\"Chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t r\u1ec5 cam th\u1ea3o c\u00f3 \u0111a c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng cho da\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Chiet-xuat-cam-thao-4.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Chiet-xuat-cam-thao-4-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Chiet-xuat-cam-thao-4-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Chiet-xuat-cam-thao-4-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8728\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t r\u1ec5 cam th\u1ea3o c\u00f3 \u0111a c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng cho da<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"luu-y-chong-chi-dinh\"><\/span><b>L\u01b0u \u00fd &amp; Ch\u1ed1ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">H\u1ea7u h\u1ebft chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t cam th\u1ea3o d\u00f9ng ngo\u00e0i da an to\u00e0n, \u00edt g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 cao ho\u1eb7c c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ecba d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ecf nh\u1eb9 ho\u1eb7c ng\u1ee9a.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m v\u1edbi nh\u00f3m th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt h\u1ecd \u0111\u1eadu (Fabaceae) n\u00ean th\u1eed test v\u00f9ng nh\u1ecf tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi d\u00f9ng di\u1ec7n r\u1ed9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tr\u00e1nh d\u00f9ng song song v\u1edbi retinoid m\u1ea1nh ho\u1eb7c acid peel n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 cao, \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m nguy c\u01a1 k\u00edch \u1ee9ng ch\u1ed3ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>Xem th\u00eam: <a href=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/tinh-chat-duong-trang-giga-gsc\/\">Serum d\u01b0\u1ee1ng tr\u1eafng s\u00e1ng GIGA WHITE<\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/tinh-chat-duong-trang-giga-gsc\/\">, <\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/tinh-chat-duong-sang-dem-mela-gsc\/\">Serum cho da n\u00e1m<\/a><\/p>\n<p><b>Ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef c\u00f3 thai v\u00e0 cho con b\u00fa c\u00f3 d\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng?<\/b><b><br \/>\n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3. Chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t cam th\u1ea3o d\u00f9ng ngo\u00e0i da \u1edf n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 an to\u00e0n, tuy nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean d\u00f9ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m u\u1ed1ng ho\u1eb7c b\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1c cao (v\u00ec glycyrrhizin li\u1ec1u cao c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng huy\u1ebft \u00e1p). V\u1edbi s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u01b0\u1ee1ng s\u00e1ng th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng, m\u1ee9c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n an to\u00e0n cho m\u1eb9 b\u1ea7u v\u00e0 m\u1eb9 cho con b\u00fa.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"luu-y-bao-quan\"><\/span><b>L\u01b0u \u00fd b\u1ea3o qu\u1ea3n<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u1ea3o qu\u1ea3n n\u01a1i kh\u00f4, m\u00e1t, tr\u00e1nh \u00e1nh n\u1eafng v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9 cao. \u0110\u1eady k\u00edn n\u1eafp sau khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi serum ho\u1eb7c essence d\u1ea1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i m\u00e0u nh\u1eb9 theo th\u1eddi gian, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u1ebfu s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>T\u00e0i li\u1ec7u tham kh\u1ea3o:<\/p>\n<p>Leslie Baumann, MD, Cosmetic Dermatology, 2nd edition, Licorice Extract &#8211; pages 281 <a href=\"https:\/\/rlmc.edu.pk\/themes\/images\/gallery\/library\/books\/Dermatology\/Baumann%20L.%20%20Cosmetic%20Dermatology%20and%20Medicine%20%202009.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https:\/\/rlmc.edu.pk\/themes\/images\/gallery\/library\/books\/Dermatology\/Baumann%20L.%20%20Cosmetic%20Dermatology%20and%20Medicine%20%202009.pdf<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>T\u1eeb h\u01a1n 2000 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, cam th\u1ea3o (Glycyrrhiza glabra) \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng trong y h\u1ecdc c\u1ed5 truy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu v\u00e0 kh\u00e1ng vi\u00eam. Trong m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t r\u1ec5 cam th\u1ea3o tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u201cng\u00f4i sao t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean\u201d gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m k\u00edch \u1ee9ng, l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":12,"featured_media":8725,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-8724","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-su-kien"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8724","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/12"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=8724"}],"version-history":[{"count":5,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8724\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":8924,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8724\/revisions\/8924"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/8725"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=8724"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=8724"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=8724"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}